{"tid":636564,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"李家超承認向司機發擬檢控通知書不近人情","createTime":"2018-04-21T04:03:34.000Z","updateTime":"2018-04-22T06:08:40.000Z","uid":81228,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"96c3f2be18a2b437c409d83aae67a9c24722959b","tid":636564,"uid":81228,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-21T04:03:34.000Z","msg":"警方以市民車輛作人肉路障後向涉事司機發擬檢控通知書，保安局局長李家超承認做法不近人情，警方正檢討做法。<br />\n<br />\n李家超又表示，政府會創造有利條件就基本法廿三條立法，但目前未有立法時間表。<br />\n<br />\n他又說不認同美國國務院的人權報告批評香港起訴遊行人士，重申政府的檢控工作並非因為遊行人士的政治背景，而是他們在遊行期間的犯法行為。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.now.com/home/local/player?newsId=303143&amp;home=1\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fhome%2Flocal%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D303143%26home%3D1&d=sQdzBtL1UQ3B5MZCQ%2FJm3jPUa9iY%2BpOmOVTB4fMSqaQ%3D&h=3e2ac825\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fhome%2Flocal%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D303143%26home%3D1&h=bc82c937\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.now.com/home/local/player?newsId=303143&amp;home=1</a>"},{"pid":"5de8c350d9b03ce767e7209e0861f67cb0807d62","tid":636564,"uid":609,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-21T04:18:26.000Z","msg":"今朝聽左個節目<br />\n<br />\n個局長真係on9到震 講野冇邏輯 俾人chok兩chok就認死狗 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 政治班子真係冇個見得人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ca12ba005ea7a52d8b46c3597e0cadd994523fc8","tid":636564,"uid":5499,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-21T04:23:27.000Z","msg":"邊撚到係不近人情，根本唔關人情事<br />\n<br />\n正確係本末倒置呀，顛倒是非"},{"pid":"aa0b29d703b37024d51f332fa5d4f7a5091c948d","tid":636564,"uid":130105,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"5de8c350d9b03ce767e7209e0861f67cb0807d62","tid":636564,"uid":609,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-21T04:18:26.000Z","msg":"今朝聽左個節目<br />\n<br />\n個局長真係on9到震 講野冇邏輯 俾人chok兩chok就認死狗 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif